node.title: Two dead in separate crashes in the Waikato
node.content: ["Two people have died in the Waikato overnight in separate car crashes.\u00a0", "The first died at the scene after their car went over a bank at around 7:30pm on Friday.\u00a0", "The second person died after their motorbike rode off the road and into a ditch.\u00a0", "They died later in hospital.\u00a0", "Police say they are still investigating exactly what happened in each crash.", "\u00a0"]
